The evidence with the title 'Rivals set to pounce on Santorum's past ' says Jan 5, 2012  ... Texas governor Rick Perry fired an opening salvo last weekend, charging that Santorum, 53, was a big spender in Congress who voted to raise the debt ceiling and approved such pork-barrel projects as Alaska's Bridge To Nowhere, a tea pot museum in North Carolina and an indoor rain forest in Iowa. 
